<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="References">References</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Official_Opposition_(New_Zealand)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5" title="Edit section: References"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<ul><li><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFBassett1982" class="citation book cs1"><a href="/wiki/Michael_Bassett" title="Michael Bassett">Bassett, Michael</a> (1982). <i>Three Party Politics in New Zealand 1911–1931</i>. Auckland: Historical Publications. <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0-86870-006-1" title="Special:BookSources/0-86870-006-1"><bdi>0-86870-006-1</bdi></a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Three+Party+Politics+in+New+Zealand+1911%E2%80%931931&amp;rft.place=Auckland&amp;rft.pub=Historical+Publications&amp;rft.date=1982&amp;rft.isbn=0-86870-006-1&amp;rft.aulast=Bassett&amp;rft.aufirst=Michael&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AOfficial+Opposition+%28New+Zealand%29" class="Z3988"></span></li></ul>
